{{Numbers}}
'''八元数'''（{{lang-en|Octonion}}）是以實數構建的8維度[[賦範可除代數|賦範可除代數]]，為[[四元数|四元数]][[结合律|非结合]]推广的[[超复数|超複數]]，通常记为'''O'''或<math>\mathbb{O}</math>。八元數的8個維度可以視為2個4維度之[[四元數|四元數]]的組合。八元數不具備[[結合律|結合律]]和[[交換律|交換律]]，但具備[[交错代数|交错代数]]的特性，並保有[[冪結合性|冪結合性]]。

也许是因为八元数的乘法不具備结合性，因此它们作為[[超複數|超複數]]而言受關注的程度較四元数低。尽管如此，八元数仍然与数学中的一些例外结构有关，其中包括例外李群。此外，八元数在诸如[[弦理论|弦理论]]、[[狭义相对论|狭义相对论]]和{{link-en|量子逻辑|Quantum logic}}中也有应用。

==歷史==

八元數第一次被描述於1843年，於一封{{link-en|约翰·格雷夫斯|John T. Graves}}給[[威廉·盧雲·哈密頓|威廉·盧雲·哈密頓]]的信中。格雷夫斯稱其為「octaves」。<ref name=sabadini2009hypercomplex>{{Cite book | title=Hypercomplex Analysis | author=Sabadini, I. and Shapiro, M. and Sommen, F. | isbn=9783764398934 | lccn=2008942605 | series=Trends in Mathematics | url=https://books.google.com/books?id=H-5v6pPpyb4C&lpg=PA168&ots=GBaIDVCCtS&dq=december%2026%2C%201843%20octonion&pg=PA168#v=onepage&q=december%2026,%201843%20octonion&f=false | year=2009 | publisher=Birkhäuser Basel | access-date=2022-04-27 | archive-date=2021-10-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211026163755/https://books.google.com/books?id=H-5v6pPpyb4C&lpg=PA168&ots=GBaIDVCCtS&dq=december%2026,%201843%20octonion&pg=PA168#v=onepage&q=december%2026,%201843%20octonion&f=false }}</ref>{{rp|168}}後來八元數由[[阿瑟·凯莱|阿瑟·凯莱]]在1845年獨自發表。<ref name="Philosophical Magazine 1845">{{Citation | first=Arthur | last=Cayley | title=On Jacobi's elliptic functions, in reply to the Rev.; and on quaternions | journal={{link-en|哲學雜誌|Philosophical Magazine|Philosophical Magazine}} | volume=26 | year=1845 | pages=208–211 | doi=10.1080/14786444508645107 | url=https://zenodo.org/record/1431049 | accessdate=2022-04-22 | archive-date=2022-04-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220422144626/https://zenodo.org/record/1431049 }}. Appendix reprinted in ''The Collected Mathematical Papers'', Johnson Reprint Co., New York, 1963, p. 127</ref>格雷夫斯發表結果的時間點比[[阿瑟·凯莱|阿瑟·凯莱]]發表的時間稍晚一些<ref>{{citation | last=Graves | journal=Phil. Mag. | volume=26 | year=1845 | pages=315–320 | title=On a Connection between the General Theory of Normal Couples and the Theory of Complete Quadratic Functions of Two Variables | url=http://zs.thulb.uni-jena.de/receive/jportal_jparticle_00207304 | doi=10.1080/14786444508645136 | accessdate=2022-04-22 | archive-date=2015-04-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150404003535/http://zs.thulb.uni-jena.de/receive/jportal_jparticle_00207304 }}</ref>。阿瑟·凯莱發表的八元數和约翰·格雷夫斯給威廉·盧雲·哈密頓的信中所提及的並無關係。阿瑟·凯莱是獨自發現八元數的，<ref name="Philosophical Magazine 1845"/>因此八元數又被稱為'''凯莱數'''或'''凯莱代數'''。哈密頓則描述了八元數被發現並描述的早期歷史。<ref>{{citation|last=Hamilton |author-link=威廉·盧雲·哈密頓|journal=Transactions of the Royal Irish Academy|volume= 21 |year=1848|pages= 338–341|title=Note, by Sir W. R. Hamilton, respecting the researches of John T. Graves, Esq.|url=https://archive.org/details/transactionsofro21iris}}</ref>

==定义==

八元数可以视为[[实数|实数]]的八元组。八元数有多種構造方式。以[[凯莱-迪克森结构|凯莱-迪克森结构]]為例，八元数可以表達為2個[[四元數|四元數]]{{math|''P''}}與{{math|''Q''}}的組合，即{{math| ''P''+''Q'' ''l'' }}或<math>p_0 + p_1i + p_2j + p_3k + \left(q_0 + q_1i + q_2j + q_3k\right)l\,</math>，其中，量{{math|''l''}}為其中一個八元数單位並滿足：<ref name="10.4236/apm.2013.31008">{{cite journal | journal=Advances in Pure Mathematics | volume=03 | issue=01 | issn=2160-0368 | date=2013 | pages=41–69 | doi=10.4236/apm.2013.31008 | url=http://www.scirp.org/journal/doi.aspx?DOI=10.4236/apm.2013.31008 | title=Meta-Invariant Operators over Cayley-Dickson Algebras and Spectra | accessdate=2022-04-22|author=S. V. Ludkovsky | archive-date=2022-04-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220427061057/https://www.scirp.org/journal/paperinformation.aspx?paperid=27352 }}</ref>
: <math>i^2 = j^2 = k^2 = l^2 = -1 \,</math>
在這種定義下每一个八元数都是'''单位八元数'''{{math|{1, ''i'', ''j'', ''k'', ''l'', ''il'', ''jl'', ''kl''}}}的[[线性组合|线性组合]]。也就是说，每一个八元数''x''都可以写成<ref name="10.15407/emodel.41.04.019"/>
:<math>x = x_0 + x_1\,i + x_2\,j + x_3\,k + x_4\,l + x_5\,il + x_6\,jl + x_7\,kl</math>
其中系数{{math|''x''<sub>''a''</sub>}}是实数。
這些八元数單位亦滿足：<ref name="10.4236/apm.2013.31008"/>
: <math>i^2 = j^2 = k^2 = l^2 = (il)^2 = (jl)^2 = (kl)^2 = -1 \,</math>
八元数的加法是把对应的系数相加，就像[[复数_(数学)|复数]]和[[四元数|四元数]]一样。根据线性，八元数的乘法完全由以下单位八元数的[[乘法表|乘法表]]来决定。<ref name="10.15407/emodel.41.04.019">{{cite journal | journal=Èlektronnoe modelirovanie | volume=41 | issue=4 | date=2019-08-08 | pages=19–34 | doi=10.15407/emodel.41.04.019 | url=https://www.emodel.org.ua/en/archive/2019/41-4/41-4-2 | title=Some Features of the Matrix Representations of the Octonions|accessdate=2022-04-22 | author=State Enterprise National Power Company “UkrEnergo”, S.I. Klipkov | archive-date=2022-04-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220422135144/https://www.emodel.org.ua/en/archive/2019/41-4/41-4-2 }}</ref>
<!-- Unfortunately, this table cannot be converted into pipe syntax, because in pipe syntax all td elements are converted to th elements if the row starts with a th element -->
